262
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:03,583
However, I can assure you
that it's rather amazing.

263
00:14:03,666 --> 00:14:04,708
Whoa!

264
00:14:04,791 --> 00:14:06,375
Now I'm super curious!

265
00:14:06,458 --> 00:14:08,958
Don't worry, it's something
you're definitely going to love.

266
00:14:09,041 --> 00:14:10,833
