271
00:14:21,625 --> 00:14:24,500
If you won't give 'em to me,
then I'll just take 'em!

272
00:14:24,583 --> 00:14:26,208
Let me at those shino-boobs!

273
00:14:26,291 --> 00:14:28,708
Hey, stop it.
Get your hands off of me!

