Look, everybody!

404
00:23:35,458 --> 00:23:37,791
Isn't my new swimsuit,
like, super sexy?

405
00:23:37,875 --> 00:23:40,041
This is a special chemical
that makes whatever

406
00:23:40,125 --> 00:23:41,791
you're wearing transparent.

407
00:23:44,875 --> 00:23:46,333
[GEKKOU chuckles]

